'''Koos Formsma''' (born 1957 in [[Leeuwarden]], [[Friesland]])<ref name=kfw/> is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] businessman and former chairman of Dutch football club [[SC Heerenveen]]. A former [[field hockey]] player from [[HC Bloemendaal]], Formsma became the club's chairman<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sc-heerenveen.nl.kpnis.nl/web/show/id=42457/contentid=3990|title=Weer een jaar "de boeken in"|date=18 October 2006}}</ref> on 1 October 2006<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sc-heerenveen.nl/web/show/id=41696/dbid=151609/typeofpage=41438|title=Heerenveen en PSV komen niet tot scoren}}</ref> after [[Riemer van der Velde]] resigned his 23-year spell at the team.<ref name=kfw>{{cite web|url=http://www.frieschdagblad.nl/index.asp?artID=25576|title=Hockeyman’ Koos Formsma wordt nieuwe voorzitter Heerenveen |author=Bert Kalteren|date=14 September 2005|publisher=Friesch Dagblad}}</ref> Formsma was also director of the company Regma Nederland, located in [[Lelystad]], which he sold to [[Canon Inc.|Canon]] in 2012.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.regma.nl/uploads/regma%20info/Regma%20Info%20maart%202006.pdf|title=Directeur van Regma wordt nieuwe voorzitter van SC-Heerenveen}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cadmagazine.nl/blog/online-artikelen/watervast-en-uv-bestendige-kleuren|title=Watervast en UV-bestendige kleuren|date=12 March 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120721044142/http://www.cadmagazine.nl/blog/online-artikelen/watervast-en-uv-bestendige-kleuren|archivedate=21 July 2012|df=}}</ref>

